Headline: Country Data Officer at Generali Italia
Summary: I currently work as the Country Data Officer for Generali Country Italy  Leading data and AI strategy, artificial intelligence and predictive models, business and network governance services, data quality and data governance policies, analytics data lake and data culture and training programs  Before Generali, I spent a decade, from 2007 to 2017, at the Boston Consulting Group. He undertook projects in ten different countries, gaining exposure to very diverse environments.
